title: TABLE TENNIS WORLD TOUR
description: Become a paddle master and play like a champion in this challenging ping pong game with realistic physics! Choose from 20 countries and battle 60 opponents from all over the world. The touch controls are super easy to learn: simply move the table tennis bat and hit the ball in the direction you want. Train spin and power shots to throw your opponent off guard, but watch out as they might do the same to you! Can you collect all trophies and win the World Tour?
